objects.name: Brute Ratel C4
objects.description: Brute Ratel C4 made its initial debut as a penetration testing tool in December 2020.  At the time, its development was a part time effort by a security engineer named Chatan Nayak (aka Paranoid Ninja) living in India.  According to his website ( [Dark Vortex](https://0xdarkvortex.dev/about/) ), Chetan amassed several years of experience working in senior red time roles across western cybersecurity vendors.  Over the past 2.5 years, Chetan introduced incremental improvements in terms of features, capabilities, support, and training.
